  "slug": "cursormod",
  "title": "Cursor Mod",
  "description": "Change your ingame cursor",
  "body": "<p>Change your ingame cursor when game reload,</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To change your cursor add a resource pack with your cursor in a PNG format in assets/minecraft/textures/gui/ (can be change with the config \"cursorLocation\") and add in config the hotspot location</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The Cursors Config Menu (1.2)</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In Forge: from the main menu&nbsp;<strong>mods/Custom Cursor Mod/Config</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In Fabric: type <strong>/cursormod</strong> into the chat</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/226/348/2018-03-24-19_48_01-parametres.png\" alt=\"CursorMod 1.2 cursors list -- A menu to select a cursor to edit\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1040\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>You can edit by clicking on the buttons every cursors</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/226/349/2018-03-24-19_51_33.png\" alt=\"CursorMod 1.2 cursor editor -- A menu to edit hotspot and file location of the cursor\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1042\" /></p>",
